'''希罗·盖拉''' (Ciro Guerra，1981年2月6日-) 是一名[[哥伦比亚|哥伦比亚]][[电影导演|电影导演]]和[[编剧|编剧]]。他执导的《The Wind Journeys》入选2009年[[戛纳电影节|戛纳电影节]]一种关注单元。<ref name="festival-cannes.com">{{cite web |url=http://www.festival-cannes.com/en/archives/ficheFilm/id/10891792/year/2009.html |title=Festival de Cannes: The Wind Journeys |accessdate=17 May 2009 |work=festival-cannes.com |archive-date=2014-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141008231741/http://www.festival-cannes.com/en/archives/ficheFilm/id/10891792/year/2009.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>2015年执导的《[[蛇之拥抱|蛇之拥抱]]》赢得[[2015年戛纳电影节|2015年戛纳电影节]]导演双周单元的艺术院线奖<ref name="Quinzaine">{{cite web |url=http://www.quinzaine-realisateurs.com/the-directors-fortnight-2015-selection-p487.html |title=The Directors' Fortnight 2015 selection! |accessdate=21 April 2015 |work=Quinzaine des Réalisateurs |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150423224901/http://www.quinzaine-realisateurs.com/the-directors-fortnight-2015-selection-p487.html |archivedate=2015年4月23日 }}</ref><ref name="Variety">{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2015/film/festivals/cannes-directors-fortnight-lineup-unveiled-1201476479/ |title=Cannes: Directors’ Fortnight Unveils 2015 Lineup |author=Justin Chang |date=21 April 2015 |accessdate=21 April 2015 |work=Variety |archive-date=2016-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113190136/http://variety.com/2015/film/festivals/cannes-directors-fortnight-lineup-unveiled-1201476479/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，并获[[第88届奥斯卡金像奖|第88届奥斯卡金像奖]]最佳外语片提名。<ref name="88nom">{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscar-nominations-2016-full-list-855670 |title=Oscar Nominations: The Complete List |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |last=Ford |first=Rebecca |date=14 January 2016 |accessdate=14 January 2016 |archive-date=2020-01-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200115093332/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/oscars-nominations-complete-list-855398 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

